<hymn_number>137</hymn_number>
<title>The Bible. Baibil. ƲIT137</title>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<aka>Chihowa ha̱ im anump</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa ha̱ im anumpa
 I̱ holisso Baibil oka,
 Isht taloa achukma ka
 Wakayʋt keho taloá.

[V2]
 Holisso, Baibil ahanchi,
 Shilombish Holitopa ya̱,
 Micha Chisʋs Klaist aiena
 I holisso bano hoke.

[V3]
 Chihowa immi hoh kia,
 Hatak yoshoba pia ha̱
 Auet pihi̱ma tok oka,
 Na̱ yukpʋt kil aiokpʋchi.

[V4]
 Baibil ʋt holitopa kʋt
 Nana moma pim i̱ shahli,
 Pimmi yoke, il ahni hosh
 Holitoblit e taloa.

[V5]
 Pi̱ki ʋba Chihowa ya̱
 Chisʋs na̱ pi Okchalinchi,
 Shilombish Holitopa ma,
 A̱hlit a pim abahanchi.

[V6]
 Pimi Shilombish, pi chu̱kʋsh,
 Aiokcha̱ya, ʋba yakni,
 Ʋba hatak, saint moma ka
 Achukmʋt pim abahanchi.

[V7]
 Pi okcha̱ya taiyakla kʋt
 Baibil il im antiashke;
 Pillikmʋt, Pi̱ki Chihowa
 Ont e pisa hinla hoke.</lyrics>
</song>